(71, 1, 'Inis the Energy of the Sea Cologne Spray, 3.3 Fluid Ounce', '', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">A sparkling, clean unisex fragrance</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Inis instantly refreshes and makes you feel close to the sea, no matter where you are</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Energizing top notes of lemon and marine, refreshing lily of the valley, and base notes of sandalwood and clove</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">In the Inis signature frosted bottle with a cap reminiscent of glass pebbles you might find on a beach</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Made in Ireland; never tested on animals; paraben free</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Amazon Ember\", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span>\r\n	<div><br />\r\n		</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<h2 class=\"default\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 4px; margin: 0px 0px 0.25em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: medium; line-heigh